name: SlimyMix
description:
This is SlimyMix. It can do the things in the pictures, and probably a lot more too, but I usually just make superhero stuff with it. I do text2img with 512x768 or 768x512, and R-ESRGAN 4x upscaler afterwards. Use krita to touch up your images before upscaling for higher quality work. The VAE I use is vae-ft-ema-560000-ema-pruned

V2 is a modified version of V1 with less of an anime focus. Both are good to use!

modelVersions.description: This is a modified version of V1, with a little less anime.
